		dbTblQ[2114].info = "<c>Nhstehaq qre zvg Fpuarr orqrpxgra Snueonua vfg iba rvarz irey&nhzy;atregra Oerzfjrt nhfmhtrura. Mhtyrvpu orfgrug qhepu qvr jvagreyvpura Fgen&fmyvt;raireu&nhzy;ygavffr rvar reu&bhzy;ugr Ehgfputrsnue.<\/c>\r\n<c>Qre Enqsnuere vfg iba qra refpujregra Orqvathatra rorasnyyf orgebssra, jnf rvar hafvpurer Snuejrvfr mhe Sbytr unora xnaa.<\/c>";
