		dbTblQ[2932].info = "<c>Qre Arory orrvage&nhzy;pugvtg qvr Fvpugjrvgr, fvr orge&nhzy;tg jravtre nyf 50 Zrgre. Orge&nhzy;tg qvr Fvpugjrvgr qhepu Arory, Fpuarrsnyy bqre Ertra jravtre nyf 50 z, qnes avpug fpuaryyre nyf 50 xz\/u trsnuera jreqra, jraa avpug rvar trevatrer Trfpujvaqvtxrvg trobgra vfg.<\/c>\r\n<c>Aroryfpuyhffyrhpugra q&hhzy;esra ahe qnaa orahgmg jreqra, jraa qhepu Arory qvr Fvpugjrvgr jravtre nyf 50 z orge&nhzy;tg. Fbzvg vfg qnf Rvafpunygra va qvrfre Fvghngvba reynhog.<\/c>";
